# ============================================================
# Mind Map Conversion Tool - Git Ignore Rules
# 思维导图多格式转换工具 - Git 忽略规则
# ============================================================

# --- Build artifacts 构建产物 ---
obj/
*.o
*.obj
*.exe

# --- IDE and editor files IDE与编辑器文件 ---
# .vscode/ is committed (contains project build tasks)
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- OS generated files 操作系统生成文件 ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# --- Debug files 调试文件 ---
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.lib
*.dll
